{"tid":2177554,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過幾年都放唔低.","createTime":"2020-08-27T20:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T02:25:57.000Z","uid":330921,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3057bde25bec566b7a3dea521660ca74ce231e9f","tid":2177554,"uid":330921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T20:18:53.000Z","msg":"由分左手之後 每一日我都好努力甘做返自己<br />\n企返起身 向前望 <br />\n唔再諗起佢 唔會再掛住佢 <br />\n其實呢五年我都知道自己一直呃自己唔再掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係真係無辦法 唔知點做好<br />\n果一種感覺真係好難受 <br />\n我而家都有拍拖 拍左一年幾 <br />\n當初岩岩一齊果陣係幾鐘意佢 <br />\n慢慢就一齊左 都好開心 雖然係比較平淡<br />\n佢都比到我想要既野 感情都好穩定<br />\n但係唔知點解呢幾年發夢都會夢到個EX<br />\n一諗起佢個心好痛 <br />\n格幾個星期 突然間無啦啦諗起個EX<br />\n但係大家都有新歡<br />\n都知無可能再一齊<br />\n我都唔知自己想點...<br />\n邊個話時間可以沖淡一切 <br />\n呃人既！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4d6b1a91b8a696d2546e445f75a16143bff304","tid":2177554,"uid":367280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T20:20:50.000Z","msg":"行動po先. 拉"},{"pid":"c656b26b84dd451ab458fec54399374a83478e42","tid":2177554,"uid":343574,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5a4d6b1a91b8a696d2546e445f75a16143bff304","tid":2177554,"uid":367280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T20:20:50.000Z","msg":"行動po先. 拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T20:21:57.000Z","msg":"戇鳩仔，呢到係感情台，唔中意就quit左佢囖"},{"pid":"9d620f11dae6959478469b9a917a438c2113bca8","tid":2177554,"uid":156818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T20:24:50.000Z","msg":"呢幾年有冇同ex有交流過"},{"pid":"67fd313f9ad6ea4d6a09ab7bf86f22412e5e844f","tid":2177554,"uid":330921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d620f11dae6959478469b9a917a438c2113bca8","tid":2177554,"uid":156818,"like":0